WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.740 --> 00:00:07.910
He's gone.

2
00:00:07.910 --> 00:00:08.980
What?

3
00:00:08.980 --> 00:00:10.980
I'm sorry for your loss.

4
00:00:10.980 --> 00:00:15.150
We need to take a shot.

5
00:00:15.150 --> 00:00:25.219
How the fuck did Jack find us?

6
00:00:25.219 --> 00:00:26.219
He's listening to me.

7
00:00:26.219 --> 00:00:28.219
Enough is enough.

8
00:00:28.219 --> 00:00:31.219
Trust me.

9
00:00:31.219 --> 00:01:01.630
You were badly hurt and passed out.

10
00:01:01.630 --> 00:01:02.630
I know.

11
00:01:02.630 --> 00:01:09.060
There's about a thousand opportunities to kill me and my mum and you didn't.

12
00:01:09.060 --> 00:01:12.180
But still you've got tragedy.

13
00:01:12.180 --> 00:01:14.819
It's my doorstep.

14
00:01:14.819 --> 00:01:15.819
How can I forgive you?

15
00:01:15.819 --> 00:01:16.819
How can I forgive myself?

16
00:01:16.819 --> 00:01:18.819
Sorry, sorry, sorry.

17
00:01:18.819 --> 00:01:19.950
Sorry.

18
00:01:19.950 --> 00:01:21.750
Sorry.

19
00:01:21.750 --> 00:01:24.780
Can you apology bring my mother back?

20
00:01:24.780 --> 00:01:25.780
I've lost her!

21
00:01:25.780 --> 00:01:27.780
I've lost her forever!

22
00:01:27.780 --> 00:01:30.189
In the end, it makes you feel any better.

23
00:01:30.189 --> 00:01:35.609
Thanks, I'm nothing.

24
00:01:35.609 --> 00:01:39.049
It could be feel better.

25
00:01:39.049 --> 00:01:40.049
She never came.

26
00:01:40.049 --> 00:01:44.459
My mum was like the strain that can't be grounded.

27
00:01:44.459 --> 00:01:47.689
Ensuring that was never completely alone.

28
00:01:47.689 --> 00:02:05.019
I know that she's gone.

29
00:02:05.019 --> 00:02:06.019
Everyone wants me to die.

30
00:02:06.019 --> 00:02:08.020
Anyways, don't do anything stupid.

31
00:02:08.020 --> 00:02:09.020
Stop!

32
00:02:10.020 --> 00:02:13.740
No, I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

33
00:02:13.740 --> 00:02:16.629
It's not my fault.

34
00:02:16.629 --> 00:02:20.520
All of this.

35
00:02:20.520 --> 00:02:22.639
It's because of me.

36
00:02:22.639 --> 00:02:23.639
It's okay.

37
00:02:23.639 --> 00:02:27.629
Just try to come down again.

38
00:02:27.629 --> 00:02:32.860
Or even.

